<H1>
<FONT COLOR="#000099">Vorticity (Spin)</FONT></H1></CENTER>
<FONT COLOR="#000099">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=+1>&nbsp; </FONT></FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT SIZE=+1>This
section explores the topic of vorticity and its role in the development
of thunderstorms.&nbsp; Vorticity is a term meteorologists use to represent
the spin within the atmosphere.&nbsp; Air may spin around either the horizontal
or vertical axes.&nbsp; Within the development of a thunderstorm the transformation
of spin around a horizontal axis to a vertical axis is essential.&nbsp;</FONT></FONT>
